data.text:
High School

Garnered VHSL Second Team All-State and 6A All-Region First Team honors as defensive back in his senior year in 2023…Named All-State Honorable Mention and Second Team All-Region in 2022…Helped lead Western Branch to a 11-3 season in 2022 and a 10-3 season in 2021, winning the Region 6A crown in 2022…Also ran track, running the 100m, 200m and 400m.

Personal

Son of Lashaun and Rashad Cook… Born on February 14, 2006… Intending to major in Business.
